\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"3283\" height=\"2188\" src=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/pexels-pixabay-247899-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5854\" style=\"width:518px;height:auto\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This Advanced <a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/mern-stack-certification\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"4160\">Certification Program<\/a> in Data Science in association with E&amp; ICT Academy IIT Guwahati opens the gateway to a future in the dynamic world of Data Science. This course is particularly designed to shape the data scientists of tomorrow and this comprehensive program has a blend of theoretical knowledge and hands-on practical experience. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Therefore, learners can master advanced data science concepts, gain proficiency with the latest tools, and have a transformative journey toward industry readiness.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Program&#8217;s commitment will extend beyond the classroom and can provide placement support and opportunities to work on captivating real-world projects. At the forefront of innovation, this course will enable the learners with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in the competitive Data Science landscape. Hence, join the program to unlock a world of possibilities in Data Science.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"the-outcome-of-the-program\">The outcome of the Program<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>a.E&amp;ICT Academy IIT Guwahati Certification<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>b.Campus Immersion at IIT Guwahati<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>c. Mentored by Industry Experts<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>d. Capstone Projects &amp; Assignments<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>e. Doubt Clearing Sessions &amp; Mentor Assistance<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>f. Placement Assistance &amp; Mock Interviews<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"academy-offering-data-science-course\">Academy Offering Data Science Course<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2890\" height=\"2064\" src=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/pexels-pixabay-261909-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5851\" style=\"width:490px;height:auto\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As an initiative of the Ministry of Electronics &amp; Information Technology (MeitY), the Academy was built by the  IIT Guwahati under the scheme of &#8216;Financial Assistance for Setting up Electronics and ICT Academies&#8217;. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The primary aim of the Academy is to give skill training to the Faculty Members (Engineering and non-engineering) in areas such as engineering &amp; ICT application. The Academy provides online advanced certification Courses in the areas of Data Science, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/data-science-vs-artificial-intelligence\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"4418\">Artificial Intelligence<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/data-science-vs-machine-learning\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"4414\">Machine Learning<\/a>, Big Data, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/what-is-cloud-computing-replacing\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"2221\">Cloud Computing<\/a>, Full Stack, and VLSI Design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"requirements-for-the-program\">Requirements For the Program<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"4240\" height=\"2832\" src=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/pexels-cottonbro-studio-4065876-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5887\" style=\"width:544px;height:auto\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This Program is available for a Diverse Range Of Individuals who are interested in  <a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/data-science-fresher-resume\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"5626\">Data Science<\/a> &amp; want to Make A Successful Career. It Is Well-Suited For<br>A) College Students who would like to expand Their Knowledge and start Their Career In This Field, And<br>B) Working Professionals looking forward to improving their Expertise and growing in Their Career.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"career-prospects-after-data-science\">Career Prospects After Data Science<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Data Scientist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Data Engineer<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Data Analyst<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Data Architect<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Business Intelligence Analyst<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Data Architect<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Database Administrator<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Machine Learning Engineer<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Marketing Analyst<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Research Analyst<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"companies-hiring-data-science-professionals\">Companies Hiring Data Science Professionals <\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2651\" height=\"3711\" src=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/pexels-rfstudio-3810792-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5978\" style=\"width:288px;height:auto\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Notably, important companies looking forward for  Data Science professionals include <a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/flipkart-grid-4-0-software-development-challenge\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"359\">Flipkart<\/a>, Microsoft, Uber, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/add-me-to-search-google\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"1236\">Google<\/a>, Ease My Trip, Ola, TESCO, and Tech Mahindra. These organizations will recognize the value of data-driven insights and employ Data Science professionals to improve their operations and decision-making processes. As the demand for data expertise continues to rise, these companies offer exciting opportunities for individuals with skills in Data Science.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"tools-required-by-data-science-professional\">Tools Required By Data Science Professional<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The tools that are commonly used in Data Science include Seaborn, OpenCV, Anaconda, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/aws-interview-questions-with-answers\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"3673\">AWS<\/a>, Jupyter, Pandas, and NumPy. These tools are instrumental in various stages of the data science workflow, from data exploration and analysis to machine learning model development and deployment. Each tool serves a specific purpose, contributing to the overall effectiveness of a data scientist&#8217;s work<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"benefits-of-the-data-science-course\">Benefits of The Data Science Course<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" src=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/pexels-karolina-grabowska-4491461-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5980\" style=\"width:434px;height:auto\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>This data Science Course provided by Skillvertex will allow you to understand the fundamental concepts and improve your domain skills. Moreover, the mock interviews will also refine those techniques for facing interviews and that could enable one to attempt interviews confidently. The interactive lessons and the personalized approach by the mentor will enable you to improve your skills.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The data Science course at SkillVertex was beyond the expectations of the Alumni. The curriculum of data science is well-designed and covers a wide range of topics from foundational concepts to advanced techniques. The hands-on projects allowed me to apply theoretical knowledge. SkillVertex&#8217;s career team will provide guidance,  from resume building to interview preparation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"conclusion\">Conclusion<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Opting for Data Science after a BSc is like giving your science skills a high-tech upgrade. It&#8217;s the doorway to unlocking insights from data, making your BSc knowledge even more powerful in today&#8217;s data-driven world.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"data-science-after-b-sc-fa-qs\"> Data Science After BSc -FAQs<\/h2>\n\n\n<div id=\"rank-math-faq\" class=\"rank-math-block\">\n<div class=\"rank-math-list \">\n<div id=\"faq-question-1703162001053\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q1. Can I be a data scientist after my BSc?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. After earning a BSc degree, pursuing a career in data science is promising. Data scientists use machine learning and advanced programming to create innovative algorithms and automate tasks.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1703162010790\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q2. What is the monthly income of a data scientist?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans.  The average salary for a Data Scientist in India is \u20b914.4 lakhs per year (equivalent to \u20b91.2 lakhs per month). These salary estimates are derived from data collected from 38.4k recent salaries of Data Scientists across various industries.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1703162021183\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q3. What is the minimum salary of a data scientist in India?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. The starting salary for a Data Scientist is INR 4.96 LPA, while the highest salary range typically falls between INR 37 LPA to 50 LPA.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Data Science After BSc Skill Vertex provides an Advanced Certification Program in Data Scie